0data%20is%20collected%20and%20turned%20into%20tokens%20that%20are%20used%20to%20improve%20Tesla's%20AI%20models.%20That%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20produces%20better%20self-driving%20software%20to%20guide%20the%20vehicles%20more%20accurately%20and%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20AI%20world%2C%20most%20companies'%20roles%20will%20be%20to%20generate%20more%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Liu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20Tesla's%20approach%20of%20putting%20as%20many%20cars%20as%20possible%20on%20the%20road%20to%20scoop%20up%20as%20much%20data%20as%20possible%20has%20been%20better%20than%20Waymo's%20strategy%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20engineers%20sat%20in%20a%20cave%20for%20years%20working%20on%20this%20in%20relative%20isolation%2C%20not%20collecting%20as%20much%20data%2C%20or%20tokens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdb8c0cd-587d-452b-b7da-511bcb5caa72%5C%22%3EMaking%20better%20business%20decisions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELiu%20shared%20another%20example%2C%20this%20time%20theoretical%3A%20How%20can%20companies%20make%20better%20business%20decisions%20by%20looking%20back%20at%20their%20process%20and%20tokenizing%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20any%20major%20decision%2C%20there's%20probably%20six%20months%20of%20back%20and%20forth%20debate%20between%20employees%20on%20Slack%20chats%2C%20Zoom%20video%20meetings%2C%20board%20meetings%2C%20and%20data%20dashboards%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20can%20now%20turn%20all%20that%20into%20tokens%20and%20use%20that%20to%20train%20an%20AI%20system%20to%20make%20better%20decisions%20in%20the%20future%20or%20to%20help%20human%20executives%20and%20employees%20make%20better%20decisions%20next%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20job%20of%20the%20company%20and%20the%20software%20is%20to%20pull%20all%20that%20out%20of%20the%20humans%20involved%20and%20turn%20that%20into%20tokens%20for%20AI%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a02a44d6-8aa7-4fc7-ba6b-0