k%20attire%20is%20hand%20or%20machine%20washable%20(on%20a%20cold%2C%20gentle%20cycle)%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20dry%20cleaning%20and%20making%20it%20easier%20and%20more%20affordable%20to%20own%20a%20luxe%20silk%20item.%20We%20put%20Quince's%20claims%20to%20the%20test%20by%20trying%20various%20products%20from%20their%20washable%20silk%20line%20by%20washing%20them%20according%20to%20the%20brand's%20instructions%20and%20wearing%20them%20for%20over%20a%20year.%20We%20found%20some%20inconsistencies%20in%20quality%20since%20one%20dress%20did%20tear%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20it%20is%20an%20accessible%20source%20for%20genuine%20silk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22617a246c-350b-4361-964d-e505adf50079%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Maxi%20Dress%5C%22%3EWashable%20Stretch%20Silk%20Tiered%20Maxi%20Dress%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mirror%20selfie%20of%20the%20author%20in%20a%20brown%20tiered%20maxi%20dress.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662fc4ad0dfb1341e90050e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20copper%20brown%20color%20was%20extremely%20versatile%20to%20dress%20up%20or%20down%2C%20but%20there%20are%20four%20other%20dark%20hues%20to%20choose%20from%20in%20sizes%20XS%20through%20XL.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Ergas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20dress%20has%20become%20my%20most-reached-for%20item%20of%20clothing%20this%20summer.%20While%20elegant%20enough%20to%20dress%20up%20with%20some%20heels%20and%20a%20clutch%20for%20dinner%2C%20I%20mostly%20pair%20it%20with%20sneakers%20for%20an%20elevated%20and%20comfortable%20daytime%20look.%20(The%20sneaker%20look%20works%20for%20me%20because%2C%20at%205-foot-7%2C%20the%20dress%20hits%20me%20right%20above%20the%20ankles%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20shorter%2C%20it%20may%20fall%20closer%20to%20the%20floor.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20particularly%20love%20the%20tiered%20A-line%20silhouette%2C%20which%20is%20very%20flattering%2C%20and%20the%20forgiving%20elastic%20high%20waist.%20The%20v-neckline%20is%20fairly%20deep%20(which%20I%20like%2C%20because%20it%20adds%20a%20feminine%20touch%20to%20balance%20out%20the%20baggier%20silhouette)%2C%20but%20I%20was%20still%20able%20to%20wear%20it%20with%20a%20bra.%20It's%20not%20see-through%20at%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20particularly%20hot%20days%2C%20I%20did%20sweat%20in%20this%20dress%20(usually%20I%20pick%20sleeveless%20items%20when%20I%20think%20I%20may%20sweat)%2C%20and%20the%20sweat%20was%20fairly%20visible%20through%20the%20silk%20fabric.%20That's%20the%20only%20downside%20I%20found%20to%20this%20dress.%20I%20washed%20it%20cold%20on%20the%20delicates%20cycle%20and%20hung%20it%20to%20dry.%20I%20steamed%20it%20to%20remove%20wrinkles%20(ironing%20silk%20is%20not%20recommended).%20Each%20time%20I%20wore%20the%20dress%20after%20washing%2C%20I%20found%20it%20as%20soft%20and%20shiny%20as%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec9ec5f8-6c10-4cb2-9ae7-eaff6483c11a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Slip%20Dress%5C%22%3E100%25%20Washable%20Silk%20Slip%20Dress%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20side%20by%20side%20images%20of%20the%20author%20in%20a%20silk%20slip%20dress%20styled%20with%20different%20sweaters.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662fae1310dfcda409645cff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20slip%20dress%20is%20available%20in%20nine%20colors%20including%20lilac%2C%20moss%20green%2C%20burgundy%2C%20and%20black.%20Here%20it%20is%20in%20champagne.%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Crozier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20midi%20length%2C%20bias%20cut%20slip%20dress%20is%20crafted%20from%20mulberry%20silk%20with%20a%20satin%20finish.%20It%20has%20adjustable%20spaghetti%20straps%2C%20and%20the%20brand%20claims%20the%20fabric%20is%20naturally%20thermoregulating%20to%20help%20maintain%20body%20temperature.%20It%20comes%20in%20nine%20colors%20in%20sizes%20XS%20through%20XL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrust%20me%2C%20nothing%20feels%20better%20than%20coming%20home%20from%20a%20long%20day%20of%20wearing%20restrictive%20clothing%20and%20putting%20on%20this%20buttery-soft%20slip.%20In%20the%20summer%2C%20this%20is%20the%20ultimate%20at-home%20outfit.%20And%20it's%20so%20incredibly%20chic%20to%20lounge%20around%20in%20a%20silk%20slip%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Samantha%20Crozier%2C%20style%20and%20beauty%20editor%20at%20Insider%20Reviews.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpdate%20after%20over%20a%20year%20of%20wear%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEven%20though%20it's%20a%20flattering%2C%20classic%20style%20that%20style%20editor%20Samantha%20Crozier%20was%20able%20to%20wash%20and%20wear%20for%20about%20nine%20months%2C%20the%20dress%20finally%20tore%20at%20a%20corner%20seam.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20it's%20an%20easy%20dress%20to%20throw%20on%2C%20with%20a%20beautiful%20sheen%20that%20makes%20you%20feel%20polished%20in%20no%20matter%20where%20you%20wear%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20highly%20affordable%20for%20genuine%20silk.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EYou're%20likely%20to%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20use%20from%20this%20dress%20before%20you%20experience%20the%20same%20disappointment.%20However%2C%20its%20shelf%20life%20does%20put%20it%20in%20the%20category%20of%20fast%20fashion%2C%20so%20we%20can't%20call%20it%20a%20sustainable%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20silk%20slip%20dress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6669e2f7ed9a404d829d082c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJaclyn%20wears%20a%201X%20on%20the%20left%2C%20and%20a%202X%20on%20the%20right%20of%20the%20Washable%20Silk%20Slip%20Dress.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20a%20gorgeous%20slip%20dress%2C%20perfect%20for%20dressing%20up%20or%20down%2C%20depending%20on%20my%20mood.%20Make%20it%20washable%2C%20and%20I'm%20in%20love.%20This%20silk%20dress%20has%20a%20nice%20bias%20cut%20down%20the%20side%20seam%20with%20extra%20room%20in%20the%20hips%2C%20showing%20that%20it%20was%20designed%20with%20curvier%20bodies%20in%20mind.%20It%20hits%20right%20below%20the%20knee.%20Adjustable%20straps%20helped%20me%20position%20the%20dress%20comfortably%20across%20my%20chest.%20Being%20in%20between%20sizes%2C%20I%20preferred%20the%20slightly%20roomier%20fit%20of%20the%202X%20to%20the%201X.%20The%201X%20felt%20too%20tight%20and%20pulled%20in%20the%20back%2C%20while%20the%202X%20was%20a%20little%20large%20under%20the%20armpits%20but%20nothing%20too%20noticeable.%20I'm%20not%20wearing%20shapewear%20in%20either%20of%20the%20photos%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Jaclyn%20Turner%2C%20senior%20home%20editor%2C%20Insider%20Reviews.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ERead%20more%20in%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fquince-plus-size-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuince%20plus%20size%20clothing%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7d967d9-05d7-46f1-9329-207349a7e1cf%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Midi%20Skirt%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWashable%20Silk%20Skirt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20in%20a%20black%20silk%20skirt%20from%20Quince.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db20ee585f1dff88b2a190%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22825%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETalia%20Ergas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%20A%20silk%20skirt%20is%20such%20a%20versatile%20wardrobe%20staple.%20It%20pairs%20well%20with%20sneakers%20and%20a%20t-shirt%20or%20slouchy%20sweater%20for%20a%20casual%20ensemble%20or%20can%20be%20worn%20with%20heels%20and%20a%20matching%20silky%20camisole%20for%20a%20dressy%20evening%20look.%20I%20was%20super%20excited%20to%20try%20Quince's%20version%2C%20which%20comes%20in%20an%20impressive%20range%20of%20nine%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20skirt%2C%20which%20hits%20just%20below%20the%20knees%2C%20did%20not%20disappoint.%20I'm%20currently%20between%20a%20medium%20and%20a%20large%20in%20bottoms%2C%20and%20sizing%20up%20to%20a%20large%20ended%20up%20being%20the%20right%20call.%20The%20elastic%20waistband%20falls%20loosely%20at%20my%20hips%20and%20the%20skirt%20is%20plenty%20flowy%2C%20so%20it%20doesn't%20show%20any%20panty%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210b0a482-20e3-46fa-8a9b-090cb88398c4%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Halter%20Top%5C%22%3E100%25%20Washable%20Silk%20Halter%20Top%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20wearing%20the%20Quince%20100%25%20Washable%20Silk%20Halter%20Top%20and%20taking%20a%20mirror%20selfie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0ef405114270019aeacfd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI'm%20usually%20between%20a%20small%20and%20a%20medium%20in%20tops%2C%20but%20I%20sized%20up%20to%20a%20medium%20here%20and%20was%20glad%20to%20have%20the%20extra%20room%20for%20that%20drapey%20look.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Ergas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20absolutely%20love%20this%20halter%20top%20as%20a%20comfortable%20and%20breezy%20option%20for%20an%20evening%20out.%20My%20favorite%20way%20to%20wear%20it%20is%20tucked%20into%20ripped%20jeans%20and%20paired%20with%20heels.%20It%20looks%20elegant%20and%20dressy.%20I%20think%20it%20would%20look%20equally%20good%20tucked%20into%20a%20pencil%20skirt%20and%20topped%20with%20a%20cardigan%20for%20days%20in%20the%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20the%20tiered%20maxi%20dress%2C%20the%20halter%20top%20washed%20well%20(in%20the%20delicates%20cycle%20and%20hung%20dry)%20and%20remained%20soft%20and%20shiny.%20The%20black%20version%20isn't%20see-through%20at%20all%2C%20although%20I'm%20not%20sure%20if%20the%20lighter%20champagne%20color%20would%20be%20(there's%20also%20a%20navy%20option).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e7c28ec-6954-4171-b472-faa6346e7369%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Stretch%20Silk%20Notch%20Collar%20Blouse%5C%22%3EWashable%20Stretch%20Silk%20Notch%20Collar%20Blouse%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20the%20side%20of%20a%20woman%20wearing%20a%20white%20silk%20blouse%20tucked%20and%20untucked%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6669e164ed9a404d829d0685%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJaclyn%20wears%20a%202x%20of%20the%20Washable%20Stretch%20Silk%20Notch%20Collar%20Blouse%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20forever%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20a%20good%20button%20down%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20love%20the%20Washable%20Stretch%20Silk%20Blouse.%20I%20typically%20size%20up%20in%20button-down%20blouses%20because%20I%20have%20a%20large%20chest.%20Sadly%2C%20the%20silk%20blouse%20in%20a%202X%20pulled%20at%20my%20chest%20and%20around%20my%20middle%2C%20making%20me%20feel%20a%20little%20too%20self-conscious.%20The%20ivory%20color%20was%20also%20quite%20sheer%2C%20and%20the%20slight%20stretch%20of%20the%20fabric%20only%20accentuated%20the%20parts%20that%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20show%20off%20more.%20Ironically%2C%20the%20model%20in%20the%20product%20photo%20wears%20the%20bottom%20half%20of%20the%20shirt%20unbuttoned%2C%20as%20a%20foreshadowing%20of%20my%20experience%2C%20while%20another%20model%20wearing%20the%20blouse%20in%20wine%20appears%20to%20be%20swimming%20in%20it.%20If%20the%20shirt%20would%20fit%20me%20right%2C%20I%20think%20it%20looks%20very%20classy%20and%20sophisticated%20and%20a%20great%20workwear%2C%20or%20day-to-night%20piece%3B%20just%20the%20sizing%20is%20off%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Jaclyn%20Turner%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3Esenior%20home%20editor%2C%20Insider%20Reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22990dd29b-e184-4b7c-9a37-6e8506325eb4%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Pajama%20Set%5C%22%3E100%25%20Washable%20Silk%20Pajama%20Tee%20and%20Pants%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20taking%20a%20mirror%20selfie%20while%20wearing%20the%20Quince%20100%25%20Washable%20Silk%20Pajama%20Tee.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0effd57bff7001947f0ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20sleep%20hot%2C%20so%20I%20appreciated%20the%20breeziness%20of%20this%20pajama%20set%3Cp%3ETalia%20Ergas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20super%20roomy%20silhouette%2C%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-cooling-pajamas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecooling%20pajama%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20is%20comfy%20and%20elegant%20for%20both%20sleeping%20and%20lounging%20around.%20You%20could%20totally%20get%20away%20with%20wearing%20the%20T-shirt%20out%20with%20a%20pair%20of%20jeans%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20huge%20benefit%20of%20this%20combo%20(both%20pieces%20available%20in%20sizes%20XS%20through%20XL)%20is%20the%20mix%20and%20matchability%20since%20the%20top%20and%20bottom%20are%20sold%20separately.%20You%20can%20pick%20different%20sizes%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20interchange%20the%20styles%20(there%20are%20also%20a%20button%20up%20shirts%2C%20a%20tank%2C%20or%20shorts%20available).%20The%20pants%2C%20shorts%2C%20tee%2C%20and%20tank%20are%20available%20in%20seven%20colors%20(sizes%20XS%20through%20XL)%2C%20while%20the%20button%20up%20top%20only%20comes%20in%20five%20colors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20picked%20a%20medium%20in%20my%20top%2C%20which%20fit%20perfectly.%20For%20the%20bottoms%2C%20I%20picked%20a%20large%20since%20I%20often%20wear%20large%20bottoms%20from%20other%20brands%20and%20have%20previously%20tried%20other%20Quince%20medium%20sweats%2C%20which%20were%20snug.%20The%20large%20was%20very%20big%20on%20me%2C%20and%20I%20wished%20I%20had%20sized%20down%20to%20a%20medium.%20I%20would%20recommend%20sizing%20down%20in%20the%20bottoms%2C%20if%20you're%20between%20sizes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20washed%20these%20in%20the%20gentle%20cycle%20and%20hung%20them%20to%20dry.%20The%20smoothness%20and%20softness%20of%20the%20fabric%20did%20not%20change%20due%20to%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20wash%20washable%20silk%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20instructions%20on%20Quince's%20website%2C%20we%20washed%20the%20garments%20in%20cold%20water%20in%20the%20delicates%20cycle%20and%20hung%20them%20to%20dry.%20We%20steamed%20the%20garments%20because%20they%20wrinkled%20easily%2C%20but%20this%20caused%20no%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227fb4294f-525d-47e3-8a66-4180e182687e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20wear%20and%20wash%20your%20silk%20casually%2C%20your%20Quince%20washable%20silk%20may%20not%20last%20you%20very%20long.%20We%20also%20found%20the%20sizing%20to%20be%20a%20little%20inconsistent%20with%20this%20line.%20While%20sizing%20up%20was%20a%20good%20choice%20in%20the%20halter%20top%20and%20tiered%20dress%2C%20it%20led%20us%20astray%20for%20the%20pajama%20pants%2C%20where%20sizing%20down%20would%20have%20fit%20better.%20Thankfully%2C%20though%2C%20Quince%20has%20a%20generous%20return%20policy%20with%20a%20full%20refund%20on%20unworn%20items%20with%20the%20tags%20on%20available%20for%20365%20days%20from%20the%20purchase%20date.%20So%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20comfortable%20to%20take%20your%20best%20guess%20at%20a%20size%20and%20return%20it%20if%20the%20fit%20isn't%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%2