ETwins%20Study%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20a%20research%20program%20involving%20former%20NASA%20astronaut%20Scott%20Kelly%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20space%20for%20nearly%20a%20year%2C%20and%20his%20identical%20twin%20brother%2C%20Mark%2C%20who%20lived%20on%20the%20ground%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Stich%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bevery%20single%20crew%20member%20that%20we%20fly%20in%20orbit%2C%20we%20collect%20medical%20research%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20drawing%20blood%2C%20measuring%20bone%20density%2C%20and%20testing%20vision%20multiple%20times%20throughout%20their%20space%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20gravity%2C%20higher%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmars-radiation-levels-spacex-nasa-exposure-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eradiation%20exposure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20space-compatible%20diet%2C%20and%20other%20facts%20of%20life%20in%20orbit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-twin-study-new-results-mark-scott-kelly-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffected%20Scott's%20body%20in%20significant%20and%20surprising%20ways.%3C%2Fa%3E%20While%20Wilmore%20and%20Williams%20weren't%20in%20space%20for%20as%20long%20as%20Scott%2C%20they%20likely%20experienced%20similar%20changes%20though%20perhaps%20not%20as%20extreme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20nine%20biological%20oddities%20that%20researchers%20have%20found%20might%20happen%20to%20your%20body%20if%20you%20live%20in%20space%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYour%20body%20fluids%20shift.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22space_7%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5aeb50e719ee864e008b483e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESkye%20Gould%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20orbit%20Earth%2C%20you're%20effectively%20in%20free-fall%20around%20the%20planet%2C%20and%20weightless.%20This%20means%20there's%20nothing%20to%20force%20blood%20and%20other%20bodily%20fluids%20toward%20your%20feet.%20The%20fluid%20shifting%20from%20your%20legs%20to%20your%20head%20in%20a%20year%20could%20fill%20a%202%20liter%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYour%20face%20looks%20different.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22space_6%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5aeb50e719ee8625008b481e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESkye%20Gould%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20less%20gravity%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20liquids%C2%A0move%20toward%20and%20into%20your%20head%20%E2%80%94%20so%20your%20face%20looks%20puffy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYour%20sight%20could%20change.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22space_5%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5aeb50e719ee8623008b483d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESkye%20Gould%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20same%20reason%20that%20your%20face%20puffs%20out%2C%20your%20vision%20might%20get%20worse%20due%20to%20pressure%20changes%20in%20the%20brain.%20Fluids%20near%20the%20optic%20nerve%20can%20push%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20eyeball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeep-space%20radiation%20might%20also%20promote%20cataracts%20and%20impair%20eyesight.%20Even%20high-flying%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-airplane-cancer-radiation-risk-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercial-airline%20workers%20face%20that%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0because%20of%20the%20thinner%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYour%20bone%20density%20can%20change.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22space_1%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insid