zes-airline-for-denying-medical-waiver-to-her-92-year-old-ailing-father-where-is-the-empathy%2Farticleshow%2F119221762.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Quad%2C%20India%20May%20Be%20Part%20Of%20New%20Military%20Grouping%20In%20South%20China%20Sea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20Quad%20steadily%20strengthens%20its%20hold%20across%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20India%20may%20soon%20consider%20being%20a%20part%20of%20another%20key%20multilateral%20alliance%20that%20focuses%20on%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%20The%20group%20in%20question%20is%20the%20'Squad'%20-%20whose%20members%20currently%20include%20Japan%2C%20Australia%2C%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20Philippines.%20The%20group%20now%20plans%20to%20invite%20India%20and%20South%20Korea%20to%20join%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhilippines%20and%20Japan%2C%20which%20face%20challenges%20with%20China's%20growing%20military%20presence%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20aim%20to%20counter%20Beijing%20and%20keep%20it%20in%20check%2C%20said%20General%20Romeo%20S.%20Brawner%2C%20the%20Philippines'%20Armed%20Forces%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Squad%20is%20still%20an%20informal%20grouping%2C%20member%20states%20have%20conducted%20joint%20maritime%20activities%20in%20South%20China%20Sea%20for%20over%20a%20year.%20%26quot%3BTogether%20with%20Japan%20and%20our%20partners%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20expand%20the%20squad%20to%20include%20India%20and%20probably%20South%20Korea%2C%26quot%3B%20General%20Brawner%20said%20at%20the%20Raisina%20Dialogue%20-%20a%20multilateral%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20General's%20comment%20on%20inviting%20India%20to%20the%20'Squad'%2C%20came%20as%20his%20counterpart%20from%20Japan%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20US%20Indo-Pacific%20Command%2C%20and%20Australia's%20chief%20of%20Joint%20Operations%20were%20on%20stage%20for%20a%20panel%20discussion%20on%20security%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Brawner%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Philippines%20was%20making%20efforts%20to%20enhance%20its%20deterrence%20capabilities%2C%20including%20by%20working%20with%20partners%20in%20the%20Squad%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20an%20informal%20collaboration%20between%20the%20four%20nations%20on%20military%20aspects%2C%20intelligence%20sharing%2C%20and%20joint%20exercises%20and%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mention%20of%20a%20possible%20invite%20to%20India%20and%20South%20Korea%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Manila%20and%20Beijing%20are%20facing%20increasing%20hostilities%20and%20a%20series%20of%20escalating%20confrontations%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20unilaterally%20claims%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20as%20its%20own%20territory%2C%20totally%20disregarding%20international%20maritime%20law.%20Beijing%20considers%20the%20entire%20sea%20as%20its%20exclusive%20economic%2C%20strategic%2C%20and%20military%20zone%20-%20something%20that%20has%20been%20shot%20down%20by%20the%20International%20and%20UN%20court%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20rejected%20the%20international%20court%20ruling%20and%20blatantly%20disregards%20it%2C%20opposing%20a%20rules-based%20global%20order.%20Beijing%20also%20disregards%20the%20sovereignty%20claims%20by%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Brunei%2C%20and%20Vietnam%20-%20all%20of%20which%20have%20coastlines%20along%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20-%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20China%20Sea%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20maritime%20trade%20routes%2C%20which%20sees%20an%20annual%20trade%20flow%20of%20more%20than%20%243%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20find%20commonality%20with%20India%20because%20we%20have%20a%20common%20enemy.%20And%20I'm%20not%20afraid%20to%20say%20that%20China%20is%20our%20common%20enemy.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20we%20collaborate%20together%2C%20maybe%20exchange%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20General%20Brawner%20told%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20Reuters%2C%20the%20General%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Philippines%20already%20had%20a%20partnership%20with%20the%20Indian%20military%20and%20defence%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20will%20extend%20an%20offer%20for%20India%20to%20join%20the%20'Squad'%20when%20he%20meets%20India's%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20or%20CDS%20General%20Anil%20Chauhan%20later%20in%20the%20day.%20After%20the%20meeting%2C%20a%20senior%20Indian%20defence%20personnel%20told%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20that%20there%20was%20no%20clarity%20yet%20if%20the%20matter%20was%20indeed%20discussed.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742404500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Flg7ok3to_indian-navy-maritime-exercise-ians_625x300_02_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-quad-india-may-be-part-of-squad-new-military-grouping-in-south-china-sea-7962505%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20as%20the%20Quad%20steadily%20strengthens%20its%20hold%20across%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20India%20may%20soon%20consider%20being%20a%20part%20of%20another%20key%20multilateral%20alliance%20that%20focuses%20on%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-quad-india-may-be-part-of-squad-new-military-grouping-in-south-china-sea-7962505%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farm%20Leaders%20Detained%20In%20Punjab's%20Mohali%2C%20Cops%20Clear%20Shambhu%20Border%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20farmer%20leaders%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20