s%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsinister-irish-rape-crisis-charity-slams-conor-mcgregor-donald-trump-meeting-calls-it-a-dangerous-message%2Famp_articleshow%2F119220080.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsinister-irish-rape-crisis-charity-slams-conor-mcgregor-donald-trump-meeting-calls-it-a-dangerous-message%2Famp_articleshow%2F119220080.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTaiyyar%20Raho%26quot%3B%3A%20100%20Lawyers%20Try%20To%20Attack%20Cement%20Murder%20Accused%20In%20Meerut%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20accused%20of%20stabbing%20her%20Merchant%20Navy%20officer%20husband%20and%20chopping%20up%20his%20body%20found%20themselves%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20ire%20of%20over%20100%20lawyers%20when%20they%20were%20produced%20in%20a%20court%20in%20Meerut%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20lawyers%20tried%20to%20assault%20the%20alleged%20killers%2C%20who%20were%20shielded%20by%20a%20team%20of%20police%20personnel%2C%20after%20they%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20courtroom%20and%20continued%20their%20efforts%20even%20after%20they%20were%20seated%20in%20a%20police%20vehicle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20angry%20lawyers%20also%20climbed%20atop%20a%20car%20to%20try%20and%20attack%20the%20woman%20and%20her%20lover.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%20Rastogi%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20Sahil%20Shukla%20were%20produced%20before%20the%20additional%20chief%20judicial%20magistrate's%20court%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20being%20arrested%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Muskaan's%20husband%2C%20Saurabh%20Rajput.%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%20had%20allegedly%20drugged%20Saurabh%20before%20stabbing%20him%20to%20death%2C%20chopping%20up%20his%20body%20into%2015%20pieces%20and%20stuffing%20it%20in%20a%20drum%20which%20they%20sealed%20with%20cement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20there%20were%20no%20issues%20when%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%20were%20being%20produced%20in%20the%20courtroom%20but%20they%20started%20receiving%20information%20that%20a%20crowd%20of%20angry%20lawyers%20had%20begun%20gathering%20in%20the%20court%20complex.%20More%20police%20personnel%20were%20called%20in%20but%20they%20found%20themselves%20facing%20at%20least%20a%20hundred-strong%20crowd%20intent%20on%20thrashing%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20show%20the%20two%20alleged%20killers%20being%20protected%20by%20police%20personnel%20as%20they%20are%20taken%20down%20the%20steps%20of%20the%20court%20towards%20the%20waiting%20lawyers.%20Shouts%20of%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Btaiyyar%20raho%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20(stay%20ready)%20and%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bmaaro%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E(attack)%20can%20be%20heard%20as%20the%20lawyers%20try%20to%20assault%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil.%20The%20lawyers%20are%20pushed%20away%20by%20the%20police%2C%20but%20a%20couple%20of%20them%20land%20blows%20before%20another%20climbs%20atop%20an%20SUV%20and%20tries%20to%20hit%20the%20alleged%20killers%20from%20above.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20personnel%20keep%20pushing%20the%20lawyers%20as%20they%20try%20and%20take%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%20towards%20a%20waiting%20police%20car.%20A%20lawyer%20manages%20to%20elbow%20one%20of%20the%20alleged%20killers%20as%20they%20are%20being%20seated%20in%20the%20car%20and%20another%20can%20be%20seen%20hitting%20them%20from%20the%20front%20passenger%20window%20of%20the%20vehicle.%20The%20car%20finally%20manages%20to%20get%20moving%2C%20leaving%20the%20crowd%20behind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(Meerut%20City)%20Ayush%20Vikram%20Singh%20said%20Saurabh's%20murder%20was%20plotted%20entirely%20by%20Muskaan%2C%20who%20conceived%20the%20plan%20in%20November%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20Muskaan%20had%20convinced%20her%20boyfriend%2C%20who%20regularly%20consumed%20narcotics%2C%20that%20his%20dead%20mother%20was%20speaking%20to%20him%20through%20a%20Snapchat%20account%20that%20she%20had%20created.%20This%20ploy%20was%20also%20used%20by%20her%20to%20ensure%20Sahil%20got%20involved%20in%20the%20murder%20plot.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20by%20Shyam%20Parmar)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742400660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fqmv1s08g_up-murder-accused-attacked_625x300_19_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmerchant-navy-officer-saurabh-rajput-muskaan-rastogi-sahil-shukla-drugs-drum-cement-drum-taiyyar-raho-100-lawyers-try-to-attack-cement-murder-accused--7962292%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20woman%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20accused%20of%20stabbing%20her%20Merchant%20Navy%20officer%20husband%20and%20chopping%20up%20his%20body%20found%20themselves%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20ire%20of%20over%20100%20lawyers%20when%20they%20were%20produced%20in%20a%20court%20in%20Meerut%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmerchant-navy-officer-saurabh-rajput-muskaan-rastogi-sahil-shukla-drugs-drum-cement-drum-taiyyar-raho-100-lawyers-try-to-attack-cement-murder-accused--7962292%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Screening%20To%20Continue%20After%20Visa%20Issuance%3A%20Why%20Indian%20Immigrants%20Are%20Worried%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERamping%20up%20its%20already%20strict%20immigration%20rules%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20has%20confirmed%20through%20its%20official%20X%20account%20that%20the%20visa%20screening%20does%20not%20stop%20after%20a%20visa%20is%20issued.%20The%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20stated%20visa%20holders%20are%20continuously%20monitored%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20complying%20with%20all%20US%20laws%20and%20immigration%20rules.%20This%20came%20along%20with%20a%20warning%20that%20those%20who%20fail%20to%20abide%20by%20these%20rules%2C%20may%20face%20revocation%20of%20visa%20or%20face%20deportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EU.S.%20visa%20screening%20does%20not%20stop%20after%20a%20visa%20is%20issued.%20We%20continuously%20check%20visa%20holders%20to%20ensure%20they%20follow%20all%20U.S.%20laws%20and%20immigration%20rules%20%E2%80%93%20and%20we%20will%20revoke%20their%20visas%20and%20deport%20them%20if%20they%20don't.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FaZsnUTnXGP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FaZsnUTnXGP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Department%20of%20State%20(%40StateDept)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStateDept%2Fstatus%2F1901639502743171373%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2017%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Green%20Card%20or%20Permanent%20Residency%20Card%20grants%20individuals%20to%20work%20and%20live%20permanently%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20However%2C%20JD%20Vance%20has%20emphasised%20that%20having%20a%20Green%20Card%20does%20not%20guarantee%20indefinite%20residency.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20Fox%20News%2C%20he%20said%20even%20if%20he%20had%20a%20favourable%20opinion%20of%20a%20Green%20Card%20holder%2C%20the%20individual%20still%20won't%20have%20an%20indefinite%20right%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department%20has%20reiterated%20this%20claim%2C%20stating%20that%20screening%20continues%20even%20after%20the%20visa%20is%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConservatives%20of%20the%20country%20are%20pushing%20for%20policies%20that%20are%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20immigrants%20-%20documented%20or%20undocumented%20-%20citing%20economic%20and%20national%20security%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20caused%20anxiety%20among%20Indian%20Green%20Card%20holders%2C%20particularly%20elderly%20people%20who%20spend%20the%20colder%20months%20in%20their%20home%20country%20and%20the%20rest%20in%20the%20US.%20Per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fscreening-doesnt-stop-when-you-get-visa-trump-adminstration-warns-immigrants%2Farticleshow%2F119212685.cms%5C%22%3ETOI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CBP%20(Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection)%20officers%20target%20such%20individuals%20upon%20their%20return%20and%20pressurise%20them%20to%20sign%20Form%20I-407.%20The%20form%20is%20used%20to%20voluntarily%20abandon%20your%20status%20as%20a%20lawful%20permanent%20resident%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20People%20who%20resist%20face%20threats%20of%20deportation%20or%20detention.%20Officials%20interpret%20such%20prolonged%20stays%20abroad%20as%20a%20sign%20they%20no%20longer%20intend%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20US%20permanently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20process%20has%20made%20people%20feel%20trapped%20and%20unable%20to%20visit%20their%20home%20country%20as%20they%20fear%20risking%20their%20status%20in%20the%20US.%20Immigration%20lawyers%20see%20this%20as%20an%20overreach%20by%20the%20CBP%20officers.%20However%2C%20elderly%20people%20might%20feel%20threatened%20to%20sign%20Form%20I-407.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20sources%20of%20legal%20immigration%20for%20the%20US%20but%20uncertainty%20about%20Green%20Card%20holders%20has%20made%20people%20unsure%20of%20going%20ahead%20with%20the%20process.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742400660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fgreen-card_625x300_1528361576745.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fscreening-to-continue-after-us-visa-issuance-why-indian-immigrants-are-worried-7962299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20stated%20visa%20holders%20are%20continuously%20monitored%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20complying%20with%20all%20US%20laws%20and%20imm