20grisly%20murder%20of%20a%20Merchant%20Navy%20officer%20in%20Meerut%2C%20whose%20body%20was%20chopped%20up%20and%20dumped%20in%20a%20drum%2C%20was%20planned%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20convinced%20her%20boyfriend%20that%20his%20mother%20was%20speaking%20to%20him%20-%20through%20Snapchat%20-%20from%20beyond%20the%20grave%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20also%20said%20that%20the%20wife%20had%20been%20planning%20her%20husband's%20murder%20since%20November.%20She%20had%20purchased%20two%20knives%2C%20telling%20the%20shopkeeper%20she%20would%20use%20them%20to%20cut%20chicken%2C%20days%20before%20her%20husband's%20return%20and%20had%20also%20pretended%20to%20have%20anxiety%20so%20she%20could%20visit%20a%20doctor%20and%20access%20the%20pills%20she%20would%20need%20to%20put%20him%20to%20sleep%20before%20killing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerchant%20Navy%20officer%20Saurabh%20Rajput%20was%20allegedly%20killed%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20Muskaan%20Rastogi%2C%20and%20Sahil%20Shukla%2C%20with%20whom%20she%20was%20having%20an%20extramarital%20affair%2C%20on%20March%204.%20Rajput's%20body%20was%20then%20chopped%20into%2015%20pieces%20and%20dumped%20in%20a%20drum%2C%20which%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeerut-saurabh-rajput-murder-cement-murder-up-woman-lover-kill-husband-body-chopped-up-sealed-with-cement-in-drum-7957211%5C%22%3Esealed%20with%20cement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20his%20killers%20tried%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20dispose%20of%20it%20without%20arousing%20suspicion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F0m4l07t8_cement-murder_625x300_19_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan's%20family%20has%20said%20that%20both%20she%20and%20Sahil%20did%20drugs%20regularly%20and%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeerut-saurabh-rajput-murder-cement-murder-she-must-be-hanged-merchant-navy-officers-in-laws-blame-daughter-7959216%5C%22%3Epossible%20reasons%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20killed%20Saurabh%20was%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bstop%20their%20drug%20sessions%26quot%3B.%20Sahil's%20dependence%20on%20drugs%20also%20made%20him%20susceptible%20to%20one%20of%20Muskaan's%20sinister%20plans%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20murder%20-%20she%20made%20an%20account%20on%20the%20social%20media%20messaging%20app%20Snapchat%20and%20managed%20to%20convince%20her%20lover%20that%20her%20dead%20mother%20was%20using%20it%20to%20speak%20to%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20account%20was%20not%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Sahil's%20mother%20but%20the%20messages%20were%20sent%20by%20Muskaan%20in%20a%20way%20that%20she%20made%20him%20believe%20that%20his%20dead%20mother%20had%20reincarnated%20and%20was%20speaking%20to%20him.%20She%20used%20this%20as%20a%20means%20of%20controlling%20Sahil%20and%2C%20later%2C%20convincing%20him%20to%20kill%20her%20husband%2C%20Saurabh.%20The%20entire%20plotting%20was%20done%20by%20Muskaan%2C%20who%20hatched%20the%20murder%20plan%20in%20November%26quot%3B%20said%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(Meerut%20City)%20Ayush%20Vikram%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElaborate%20Plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20that%20after%20deciding%20to%20kill%20Saurabh%2C%20Muskaan%20began%20scouting%20for%20places%20where%20she%20could%20bury%20his%20body.%20She%20told%20her%20friends%20she%20needed%20to%20bury%20some%20material%20she%20had%20used%20in%20a%20puja%20(prayer%20ritual)%20and%20even%20asked%20where%20one%20could%20bury%20a%20body.%20But%20the%20friends%20did%20not%20help%20her%20find%20a%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20said%2C%20then%20found%20out%20that%20Saurabh%2C%20who%20had%20been%20working%20in%20London%20since%202023%2C%20would%20return%20to%20Meerut%20in%20February%20to%20celebrate%20the%20birthday%20of%20their%20six-year-old%20daughter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20February%2022%2C%20she%20bought%20two%20knives%20for%20Rs%20800%2C%20saying%20she%20needed%20them%20to%20cut%20chicken.%20She%20also%20pretended%20to%20have%20anxiety%20and%20went%20to%20a%20doctor%20to%20get%20a%20prescription.%20She%20then%20looked%20up%20the%20names%20of%20two%20medicines%20online%20that%20she%20could%20use%20to%20render%20Saurabh%20unconscious%20and%20added%20them%20to%20the%20prescription%20so%20she%20could%20purchase%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20said%20that%20Saurabh%20returned%20on%20February%2024%20and%2C%20the%20next%20day%2C%20Muskaan%20mixed%20the%20medicines%20in%20his%20alcohol%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%20and%20Sahil%20kept%20looking%20for%20an%20opportunity%20and%20stabbed%20Saurabh%20to%20death%20after%20drugging%20him%20on%20March%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFailed%20Gambit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh's%20family%20had%20not%20been%20on%20good%20terms%20with%20him%20since%20he%20had%20married%20Muskaan%20against%20their%20wish%20in%202016%20and%20then%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20house%20to%20live%20with%20her%20in%20a%20rented%20apartment.%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20this%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20used%20to%20drink%20regularly%20had%20led%20to%20his%20family%20practically%20disowning%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20used%20to%20go%20to%20his%20parents'%20house%20to%20eat%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20have%20much%20of%20a%20relationship.%20He%20used%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20city%20for%20days%20and%20had%20been%20abroad%20for%20two%20years%2C%20but%20his%20family%20did%20not%20contact%20him%20much.%20Muskaan%20knew%20about%20this%20and%20she%20was%20banking%20on%20it%20to%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20the%20family%20after%20killing%20and%20burying%20him%20that%20he%20had%20gone%20abroad%20and%20would%20not%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20officer%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fooh3t1to_meerut-cement-murder_625x300_19_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20killing%20Saurabh%2C%20Muskaan%20told%20everyone%20that%20he%20had%20gone%20to%20a%20hill%20station.%20She%20then%20went%20to%20Manali%20with%20Sahil%20and%20uploaded%20photos%20from%20Saurabh's%20phone%20to%20lend%20weight%20to%20her%20story.%20She%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeerut-saurabh-rajput-murder-cement-murder-merchant-navy-officers-whatsapp-chat-with-sister-days-after-his-murder-7960140%5C%22%3Eexchanged%20texts%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20members%20of%20Saurabh's%20family%2C%20including%20his%20sister%2C%20but%20the%20plan%20unravelled%20when%20they%20became%20suspicious%20that%20he%20wasn't%20answering%20their%20calls.%20They%20then%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20and%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%20were%20arrested%20when%20they%20returned%20from%20Manali%20and%20she%20confessed%20to%20her%20parents%20that%20she%20had%20killed%20Saurabh.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EDrug%20Den%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahil's%20rented%20home%2C%20which%20he%20shared%20with%20two%20other%20men%2C%20has%20several%20drawings%20on%20the%20wall%20which%20point%20to%20its%20occupants%20being%20into%20narcotics.%20A%20video%20shows%20a%20mural%20depicting%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20Satan%20with%20the%20number%206%20arranged%20around%20a%20star%20polygon.%20Several%20beer%20cans%20can%20be%20seen%20lying%20on%20the%20floor%20next%20to%20another%20mural%20reading%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20trip%20with%20us...%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%