ccessibility%20at%20the%20time%20of%20their%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20order%20came%20following%20a%20petition%20by%20two%20visually%20impaired%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Bajaj%2C%20the%20advocate%20appearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20petitioner%2C%20told%20NDTV%20that%20Rapido%20provided%20a%20summary%20of%20an%20accessibility%20audit%20report%20which%20they%20claim%20they%20received%20yesterday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20report%20showed%20that%20there%20are%20170%20accessibility%20errors%20in%20the%20platform%20at%20the%20base%20level%20of%20WCAG%20level%20A.%20It%20also%20showed%2081%20major%20failures%20in%20the%20accessibility%20of%20the%20app%2C%20and%20this%20is%20as%20per%20their%20own%20audit.%20Quite%20apart%20from%20the%20concerns%20that%20we%20got%20from%20disabled%20users%20which%20we%20were%20also%20carrying%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bajaj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERapido%20had%20argued%20that%20they%20are%20a%20small%20start-up%20in%20India%20and%20do%20not%20have%20the%20funds%20for%20this.%20The%20court%20dismissed%20the%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742395200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-03%2Fejejc97s_rapido-ev-bike-taxi-service_625x300_24_March_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fimprove-accessibility-for-disabled-or-pack-up-high-court-to-rapido-7961619%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22App-based%20transport%20aggregator%20Rapido%20has%20got%20a%20stern%20message%20from%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20demanded%20that%20it%20improve%20accessibility%20for%20disabled%20persons%20and%20stop%20operations%20till%20that%20is%20done.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fimprove-accessibility-for-disabled-or-pack-up-high-court-to-rapido-7961619%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Abductions%2C%20Disappearances%20By%20Pak%20Army%20Surge%20Across%20Balochistan%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAbductions%20and%20enforced%20disappearances%20of%20Balochis%2C%20reportedly%20by%20the%20Pakistani%20military%20establishment%20and%20its%20notorious%20spy%20agency%20ISI%20have%20taken%20a%20sharp%20upturn%20across%20Balochistan.%20Boys%20as%20young%20as%2011%20are%20allegedly%20being%20abducted%20as%20gross%20human%20rights%20violations%20continue%2C%20local%20news%20outlets%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Baloch%20Yakjehti%20Committee%2C%20a%20human%20rights%20organisation%2C%20has%20confirmed%20the%20identities%20of%2011%20Baloch%20nationals%2C%20including%20three%20minors%2C%20who%20disappeared%20after%20being%20forcibly%20abducted%20by%20Pakistani%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20Balochistan%20Post%2C%20the%20abductions%20happened%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20March%2016%20from%20near%20SBK%20University%20in%20Balochistan's%20Nushki%20district.%20Though%20several%20dozen%20people%20from%20the%20area%20were%20abducted%2C%20the%20identities%20of%2011%20have%20so%20far%20been%20confirmed.%20The%20group%20of%20abducted%20individuals%20includes%20residents%20of%20the%20town%2C%20including%20labourers%2C%20drivers%2C%20and%20even%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20more%20people%20are%20missing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20human%20rights%20group%2C%20raising%20concerns%20over%20the%20fear%20and%20distress%20among%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20have%20disappeared%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20local%20community%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Baloch%20Yakjehti%20Committee%20emphasised%20that%20the%20abduction%20and%20disappearance%20of%20minors%20and%20innocent%20civilians%20is%20a%20gross%20violation%20of%20human%20rights.%20It%20has%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20international%20human%20rights%20organisations%20to%20%26quot%3Bintervene%20urgently%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%20in%20Balochistan%20Post%2C%20those%20identified%20as%20victims%20of%20forced%20abductions%20and%20disappearances%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELiaqat%20Baloch%2C%20a%20student%20in%20class%206%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdnan%20Baloch%20from%20Ghareebabad%20in%20Nushki%2C%20another%20student%20in%20grade%206%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EZia%20ur%20Rehman%2C%20also%20from%20Ghareebabad%2C%20Nushki%2C%20a%20student%20in%20class%207%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMuhammad%20Usman%20Baloch%20from%20Zorabad%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EZubair%20Ahmed%20from%20Chagai%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAtta%20ur%20Rehman%2C%20also%20from%20Chagai%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUmar%20Shah%20from%20Padag%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETahir%20Khan%2C%20also%20from%20Padag%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHafiz%20Shakoor%20from%20Chagai%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJaleel%20Ahmed%2C%20from%20Kalat%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESanaullah%2C%20from%20Quetta%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnforced%20disappearances%20across%20Balochistan%20have%20become%20a%20recurring%20problem.%20In%202025%20there%20has%20been%20a%20surge%20in%20both%20abductions%20as%20well%20as%20extrajudicial%20killings.%20The%20residents%20of%20Balochistan%20live%20in%20fear%20amid%20reports%20of%20brutality%20by%20Pakistan's%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman%20rights%20groups%20have%20repeatedly%20urged%20Pakistani%20authorities%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20these%20torturous%20practices%20and%20has%20appealed%20for%20accountability.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20such%20incidents%20persist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalochistan%2C%20now%20a%20province%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20has%20never%20accepted%20Pakistan's%20%26quot%3Bforceful%20occupation%26quot%3B%20since%201947.%20Political%20groups%20as%20well%20as%20armed%20ones%20have%20been%20a%20war%20with%20the%20Pakistani%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20BRIEF%20HISTORY%20OF%20BALOCHISTAN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalochistan%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Kalat%2C%20had%20declared%20itself%20a%20sovereign%20nation%20after%20its%20gained%20independence%20from%20British%20India%20on%20August%205%2C%201947.%20It%20was%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%20who%20was%20the%20lawyer%20and%20legal%20adviser%20of%20Khan%20Mir%20Ahmed%20Yar%20Khan%20-%20the%20'Khan%20of%20Kalat'%2C%20and%20had%20fought%20the%20legal%20cause%20for%20Kalat's%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%204%2C%201947%2C%20a%20meeting%20was%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20which%20was%20chaired%20by%20then%20British%20Viceroy%20to%20India%2C%20Lord%20Mountbatten%2C%20and%20was%20attended%20by%20the%20then%20Khan%20of%20Kalat%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Kalat%2C%20Muslim%20League%20chief%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%2C%20and%20head%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%20Kalat%20was%20given%20three%20choices%20-%20join%20India%2C%20join%20Pakistan%2C%20or%20seek%20an%20independent%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Khan%20of%20Kalat%20chose%20an%20independent%20nation%2C%20and%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%20supported%20the%20Khan%20of%20Kalat's%20decision.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20it%20was%20agreed%20in%20that%20meeting%20that%20Kalat%20would%20become%20an%20independent%20country%20from%20August%205%2C%201947.%20Jinnah%20insisted%20that%20the%20regions%20of%20Kharan%2C%20Las%20Bela%2C%20and%20Makaran%20merge%20with%20princely%20state%20of%20Kalat%20to%20form%20a%20complete%20and%20independent%20nation%20of%20Balochistan%20-%20they%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%20with%20the%20Khan%20of%20Kalat%20Mir%20Ahmed%20Yar%20Khan%20(Photo%20Credit%3A%20Facebook%2FLofmountains%20%2F%20Travel%20Balochistan)%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%20with%20the%20Khan%20of%20Kalat%20Mir%20Ahmed%20Yar%20Khan%20(Photo%20Credit%3A%20Facebook%2FLofmountains%20%2F%20Travel%20Balochistan)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F0mnfgaf4_jinnah-with-khan-of-kalat-mir-ahmed-yar-khan-facebook_625x300_19_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3EMuhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%20with%20the%20Khan%20of%20Kalat%20Mir%20Ahmed%20Yar%20Khan%20(Photo%20Credit%3A%20Facebook%2FLofmountains%20%2F%20Travel%20Balochistan)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJinnah's%20Muslim%20League%20then%20officially%20signed%20a%20treaty%20with%20Kalat%20on%20August%2011%2C%201947%2C%20which%20recognised%20Kalat%20as%20an%20independent%20country.%20But%20months%20later%2C%20on%20March%2026%2C%201948%2C%20Jinnah%20ordered%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%20to%20move%20into%20Kalat%20(Balochistan)%20to%20forcibly%20make%20it%20a%20part%20of%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20on%20March%2027%2C%201948%2C%20in%20a%20news%20bulletin%20on%20All%20India%20Radio%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20the%20Khan%20of%20Kalat%20approached%20India%20to%20merge%20with%20it%20after%20Balochistan's%20parliament%20unanimously%20rejected%20joining%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20New%20Delhi%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20in%20a%20position%26quot%3B%20to%20accept%20it%2C%20said%20then%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20States%20VP%20Menon.%20However%2C%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Sardar%20Patel%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20this%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3E(Inputs%20from%20ANI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742395080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fg168mp1k_balochistan-protest-over-abductions-disappearances-ani_625x300_19_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fabductions-disappearances-by-pakistan-army-surge-across-balochistan-report-7961456%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abductions%20and%20enforced%20disappearances%20of%20Balochis%2C%20reportedly%20by%20the%20Pakistani%20military%20establishment%20and%20its%20notorious%20spy%20agency%20ISI%20have%20taken%20a%20sha