%20Choksi%20Explains%20Why%20He%20Isn't%20In%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202021%20he%20went%20'missing'%20from%20Antigua%2C%20sparking%20speculation%20he%20had%20been%20'kidnapped'%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20-%20an%20absurd%20claim%20proven%20false%20after%20he%20was%20found%20on%20another%20Caribbean%20island%20nation%20-%20Dominica.%20There%20were%20also%20suggestions%20he%20attempted%20to%20flee%20expecting%20extradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmehul-choksi-dominica-withdraws-case-against-fugitive-mehul-choksi-over-illegal-entry-2995792%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDominica%20Withdraws%20Case%20Against%20Mehul%20Choksi%20Over%20%26quot%3BIllegal%20Entry%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20arrested%20by%20Dominican%20authorities%20for%20entering%20their%20country%20illegally%2C%20but%20returned%20to%20Antigua%20on%20interim%20bail%20for%20medical%20treatment.%20In%20May%202022%20proceedings%20against%20him%20were%20%26quot%3Bdiscontinued%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Choksi%20had%20contested%20the%20illegal%20entry%20charge%2C%20claiming%20he%20had%20been%20from%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Antigua%20-%20called%20Jolly%20Roger%2C%20which%20he%20reportedly%20owned%20-%20by%20'cops'%20and%20taken%20to%20Dominica%20on%20a%20boat%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvijay-mallya-nirav-modi-mehul-choksi-15-000-crore-of-vijay-mallya-nirav-modis-assets-restored-to-banks-centre-7276322%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E15%2C000%20Crore%20Of%20Mallya%2C%20Modi%2C%20Choksi%20's%20Assets%20Restored%20To%20Banks%3A%20Centre%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20last%20year%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20told%20Parliament%20properties%20worth%20Rs%2022%2C280%20crore%20had%20been%20restored%20or%20sold%20off%20to%