ke%20after%20its%20third%20consecutive%20victory%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20last%20year.%20The%20mayoral%20poll%20in%20Manesar%20was%20won%20by%20an%20independent%2C%20closely%20trailed%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20ending%20up%20a%20distant%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problems%20in%20the%20faction-ridden%20Haryana%20Congress%20compounded%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20assembly%20loss%E2%80%94which%2C%20ironically%2C%20it%20was%20widely%20tipped%20to%20win%20following%20the%20turnaround%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EActing%20On%20Expected%20Lines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20choosing%20to%20fight%20the%20municipal%20polls%20on%20the%20party%20symbol%20in%20order%20to%20galvanise%20voters%20is%20what%20backfired%20on%20the%20already%20beleaguered%20Congress%20this%20time.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20the%20party%20did%20not%20field%20candidates%20for%20municipal%20polls%20on%20the%20party%20symbol%2C%20a%20technicality%20that%20gave%20it%20some%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spate%20of%20desertions%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls%20also%20added%20to%20its%20woes.%C2%A0Notable%20leaders%20such%20as%20Ram%20Niwas%20Rara%2C%20Tarlochan%20Singh%20and%20Bishan%20Lal%20Saini%20were%20among%20the%2030-odd%20leaders%20who%20switched%20camps%20ahead%20of%20the%20election.%20Rara%20had%20sought%20a%20ticket%20for%20the%20mayoral%20post%20from%20the%20Congress%20in%20Hissar.%20After%20the%20party%20denied%20this%20to%20him%2C%20he%20filed%20his%20nomination%20as%20an%20independent%E2%80%94before%20the%20BJP%20got%20him%20on%20board.%20As%20for%20Tarlochan%20Singh%2C%20in%202019%20and%20in%20the%202024%20by-election%2C%20respectively%2C%20he%20had%20been%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20in%20Karnal%20against%20former%20chief%20ministers%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20and%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini.%20The%20third%20leader%2C%20Bishan%20Lal%20Saini%2C%20a%20two-time%20MLA%20from%20Radaur%2C%20lost%20the%202024%20election%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%202014%2C%20when%20Ashok%20Tanwar%20replaced%20Phool%20Chand%20Mullana%20as%20the%20Haryana%20Congress%20chief%2C%20the%20Congress%20organisation%20in%20the%20state%20has%20been%20in%20a%20shambles.%20There%20are%20no%20permanent%20office-bearers%2C%20down%20to%20the%20block%20level%2C%20leaving%20the%20party%20to%20come%20up%20with%20ad-hoc%20lists%20before%20every%20election.%20This%20has%20been%20mostly%20on%20account%20of%20the%20turf%20wars%20between%20former%20chief%20minister%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20and%20the%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20chiefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20Uday%20Bhan%2C%20the%20incumbent%20backed%20by%20Hooda%2C%20was%20named%20as%20PCC%20chief%20in%202022%2C%20a%20proper%20organisational%20structure%20could%20not%20be%20evolved.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20rout%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20Bhan%20had%20even%20come%20up%20with%20a%20list%20of%20office-bearers%20for%20the%20municipal%20polls%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20receive%20an%20official%20nod%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20consultation%20with%20the%20rival%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Deepak%20Babaria%2C%20the%20general%20secretary%20in-charge%20of%20the%20state%2C%20proposed%20another%20list%2C%20which%20the%20Hood%20camp%20shot%20down.%20Just%20before%20the%20polls%2C%20Babaria%20was%20replaced%20as%20the%20general%20secretary%20by%20B.K.%20Hariprasad.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20Hooda%20did%20not%20even%20campaign%20for%20the%20party%20in%20the%20polls%2C%20possibly%20as%20a%20face-saving%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMissing%20Case%20of%20LoP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20snatched%20defeat%20from%20the%20jaws%20of%20victory%20in%20Haryana%20last%20year.%20But%20it%20has%20failed%20to%20course-correct.%20Months%20after%20the%20government%20formation%20and%20even%20after%20three%20sittings%20of%20the%20assembly%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20named%20a%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20(LoP)%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Haryana%20Congress%20is%20dominated%20by%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%2C%20with%2032%20of%20the%2037%20legislators%20backing%20the%20two-term%20chief%20minister%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20being%20aligned%20with%20the%20camp%20led%20by%20Kumari%20Shelja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHooda's%20hubris%20and%20high-handedness%20are%20widely%20seen%20to%20be%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20Congress's%20loss%20last%20year.%20As%20many%20as%2072%20of%20the%2090%20tickets%20were%20allocated%20according%20to%20his%20wishes.%20Hooda%20and%20Shelja%20were%20sniping%20at%20each%20other%20publicly%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls%2C%20and%20even%20a%20handshake%20initiated%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20public%20betrayed%20the%20discomfort%20between%20them.%20This%20rift%20gave%20ammunition%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%94initially%20almost%20resigned%20to%20a%20defeat%E2%80%94to%20convert%20this%20election%20into%20a%20Jat-versus-non-Jat%20campaign%2C%20which%20ultimately%20decided%20the%20contest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20given%20Hooda%20free%20rein%2C%20the%20Congress%20now%20urgently%20needs%20to%20fix%20responsibility.%20That%20means%20ensuring%20that%20the%20LoP%20position%20is%20given%20to%20a%20leader%20not%20from%20the%20Hooda%20camp%2C%20to%20counterbalance%20the%20PCC%20chief.%20Hooda%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20is%20naturally%20not%20willing%20to%20relent.%20He%20is%20keen%20on%20having%20someone%20from%20his%20own%20camp%20as%20the%20LoP%2C%20if%20not%20himself%3B%20names%20of%20veterans%20such%20as%20Ashok%20Arora%20and%20Geeta%20Bhukkal%E2%80%94a%20Dalit%20leader%E2%80%94have%20already%20been%20proposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Counterbalance%20to%20Hooda%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%2C%20it%20is%20keen%20to%20install%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Chander%20Mohan%20as%20the%20LoP%2C%20who%20revived%20his%20floundering%20career%20by%20winning%20an%20election%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202005.%20Mohan%2C%20a%20five-time%20MLA%20and%20elder%20son%20of%20Haryana's%20most%20famous%20chief%20minister%2C%20Bhajan%20Lal%2C%20was%20deposed%20under%20ignominious%20circumstances%20in%202008.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leadership%20reckons%20that%20nominating%20Mohan%20as%20LoP%20will%20also%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20his%20younger%20brother%2C%20Kuldeep%20Bishnoi%2C%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20party.%20While%20Bishnoi%20has%20been%20sidelined%20ever%20since%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20his%20son%2C%20Bhavya%2C%20lost%20the%20family%20bastion%20of%20Adampur%20on%20the%20saffron%20party's%20ticket%20in%20last%20year's%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20realisation%20has%20finally%20dawned%20on%20the%20Congress%20top%20brass%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20trim%20down%20Hooda's%20grip%20over%20the%20party%20in%20Haryana.%20More%20importantly%2C%20it%20has%20realised%20that%20this%20task%20can't%20be%20accomplished%20by%20Shelja%20alone.%20Ever%20since%20he%20became%20chief%20minister%20in%202005%2C%20Hooda%20has%20meticulously%20ensured%20the%20ouster%20or%20marginalisation%20of%20his%20opponents%20in%20the%20party%E2%80%94especially%20the%20political%20clans%20that%20have%20had%20a%20long%20association%20with%20the%20Congress.%20Veterans%20such%20as%20Bhajan%20Lal%2C%20Birender%20Singh%20and%20Rao%20Inderjeet%20Singh%20quit%20the%20party%20during%20his%20two%20chief%20ministerial%20terms%20from%202005%20to%202015.%20In%20the%20months%20preceding%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%202024%2C%20former%20LoP%20Kiran%20Choudhry%20and%20Shruti%20Choudhry%20of%20the%20Bansi%20Lal%20clan%20had%20also%20quit%20the%20Congress%2C%20again%20on%20account%20of%20Hooda's%20domination%20(Choudhry%20is%20a%20minister%20in%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini's%20government%20today).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20A%20'Jat%20Party'%20Now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHooda's%20domination%20has%20only%20ended%20up%20projecting%20the%20Congress%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Jat%20party'%20in%20Haryana%2C%20seriously%20hampering%20its%20earlier%20image%20of%20being%20an%20umbrella%20party%20that%20catered%20to%20various%20stakeholders.%20That%2018%20of%20the%2021%20OBC%20faces%20the%20Congress%20fielded%20lost%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20with%20all%20seven%20of%20its%20candidates%20being%20routed%20in%20the%20Yadav-dominated%20Ahirwal%20belt%2C%20is%20a%20story%20that%20merits%20attention.%20Congress%20veteran%20Ajay%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20the%20Ahirwal%20region%2C%20even%20quit%20the%20party%20after%20the%20election%20protesting%20his%20sidelining%2C%20though%20eventually%2C%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20managed%20to%20persuade%20him%20to%20return.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trouble%20with%20the%20Congress%20high%20command's%20plan%20to%20anoint%20Chander%20Mohan%20as%20LoP%20is%20that%20Hooda%20is%20unlikely%20to%20extend%20his%20cooperation%20to%20his%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20party%20relies%20on%20Hooda%20to%20get%20crowds%20to%20New%20Delhi%20for%20various%20protests%2C%20and%20is%20thus%20careful%20about%20not%20rubbing%20the%20veteran%20the%20wrong%20way.%20Hooda%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20a%20leader%20with%20a%20formidable%20mass%20appeal%2C%20and%20he%20cannot%20be%20taken%20lightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%2C%20though%2C%20remains%20that%20the%20Haryana%20Congress%20cannot%20be%20in%20a%20state%20of%20inertia%20for%20long.%20Changes%20have%20to%20be%20rung%20in%20if%20it%20needs%20to%20move%20ahead.%20It's%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20having%20a%20free%20run%20in%20the%20assembly%20without%20an%20LoP%2C%20and%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%2C%20coming%20into%20his%20own%20as%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20the%20bargain%2C%20who%20are%20ultimately%20benefiting%20from%20the%20Congress's%20steady%20decay%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anand%20Kochukudy%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742390760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F4kaif8s8_hooda_625x300_19_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongresss-hooda-shaped-problem-in-haryana-is-growing-7960898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20party's%20rout%20in%20the%20Haryana%20municipal%20election%2C%20held%20less%20than%20six%20months%20after%20the%20assembly%20polls%20it%20was%20sure%20to%20win%20but%20didn't%2C%20is%20telling%20of%20a%20steady%20decay.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongresss-hooda-shaped-problem-in-haryana-is-growing-7960898%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Screening%20doesn't%20stop%20when%20you%20get%20visa%3A%20Trump%20adminstration%20warns%20immigrants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742389724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119214452%2Cimgsize-1099937.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fscreening-doesnt-stop-when-you-get-visa-trump-adminstration-warns-immigrants%2Farticleshow%2F119212685.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119212685.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThis%20heightened%20scrutiny%20has%20particularly%20affected%20Indian%20Green%20Card%20holders%2C%20especially%20elderly%20individuals%20who%20spend%20extended%20periods%20in%20India%20during%20the%20winter%20months.%20Reports%20indicate%20that%20US%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20(CBP)%20officers%20have%20been%20pressuring%20these%20individuals%20at%20air