%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Beyond%20re-enrolling%20dropouts%2C%20Malik%20is%20working%20to%20bridge%20the%20digital%20literacy%20gap%20and%20provide%20sustainable%20education%20opportunities%20for%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20children.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-1200x1200.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-800x800.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956-96x96.jpg%2096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742181956.jpg%201440w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-413767%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBeyond%20re-enrolling%20dropouts%2C%20Malik%20is%20working%20to%20bridge%20the%20digital%20literacy%20gap%20and%20provide%20sustainable%20education%20opportunities%20for%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20of%20school%20dropouts%20is%20widespread.%20According%20to%20official%20data%20from%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20government%2C%20the%20tribal%20community%20and%20other%20marginalised%20communities%20have%20the%20highest%20school%20dropout%20rate%20at%20the%20secondary%20level%2C%20with%2014.17%25.%20This%20includes%2019.05%25%20among%20girls%20and%2010.55%25%20among%20boys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfshana%20Gul%2C%20a%20teacher%20in%20Uri%2C%20North%20Kashmir%2C%20has%20witnessed%20this%20harsh%20reality%20firsthand.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20wants%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school%2C%20but%20financial%20hardships%20force%20many%20to%20do%20so%2C%20especially%20girls.%20It%20is%20heartbreaking%20to%20see%20bright%20students%20leave%20their%20education%20midway%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20teacher%2C%20nothing%20hurts%20you%20more%20than%20seeing%20one%20of%20your%20bright%20students%20drop%20out%20midway.%20Some%20of%20my%20best%20students%20from%20three%20years%20ago%20are%20now%20at%20home%2C%20unable%20to%20continue%20their%20studies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20Malik%20remains%20determined.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20your%20intentions%20are%20clear%2C%20there%20will%20be%20support%20for%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20His%20initiative%20runs%20entirely%20on%20crowdfunding%2C%20with%20people%20contributing%20small%20amounts%20%E2%80%94%20Rs%20100%2C%20Rs%20200%2C%20or%20Rs%20500%20per%20month.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20people%20have%20trust%20in%20me%2C%20and%20these%20small%20contributions%2C%20though%20minimal%20for%20them%2C%20help%20us%20enrol%20students%20and%20fulfil%20their%20dreams.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20support%20for%20us%20from%20the%20government%2C%20but%20we%20do%20awareness%20sessions%20in%20tribal%20areas%20to%20educate%20people%20about%20labour%20government%20schemes%20and%20their%20importance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20schooling%3A%20Empowering%20communities%20for%20long-term%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20education%2C%20Malik%20also%20focuses%20on%20empowering%20tribal%20women%20by%20helping%20them%20acquire%20vocational%20skills%20through%20various%20government%20schemes.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20people%20in%20tribal%20areas%20are%20unaware%20of%20the%20resources%20available%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20conduct%20awareness%20programmes%20and%20guide%20them%20on%20how%20they%20can%20learn%20new%20skills%20and%20earn%20a%20livelihood.%20When%20parents%20are%20skillful%20and%20earning%2C%20it%20directly%20impacts%20the%20child%2C%20as%20he%20gets%20support%20for%20his%20education.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadiya%2C%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20benefited%20from%20one%20such%20initiative%2C%20shares%20her%20experience%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20took%20part%20in%20the%20three-month%20stitching%20work%20last%20year%20after%20an%20awareness%20programme%20in%20our%20village%20under%20the%20skill%20development%20programme.%20Now%20I%20earn%20Rs%20300-400%20a%20day%2C%20which%20is%20enough%20for%20us%20instead%20of%20doing%20nothing%20for%20gi