ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742182137-768x650.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742182137-1200x1016.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0001-1-1742182137-150x127.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-413773%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221219%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKifayatullah%20Malik%20is%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20prestigious%20President%E2%80%99s%20Award%20for%20National%20Social%20Service%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20ambitions%20do%20not%20stop%20here.%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20mission%20is%20to%20bridge%20the%20digital%20literacy%20gap%20and%20ensure%20basic%20education%20for%20all%20tribal%20children%20who%20left%20their%20education%20midway%20because%20of%20poverty.%20He%20plans%20to%20expand%20his%20efforts%20beyond%20North%20Kashmir%20and%20sustain%20his%20initiatives%20through%20NGO%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20child%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20they%20come%20from%2C%20deserves%20a%20chance%20to%20learn.%20I%20will%20keep%20working%20until%20every%20tribal%20child%20has%20access%20to%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20dedication%20has%20earned%20him%20several%20prestigious%20accolades%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20President%E2%80%99s%20Award%20for%20National%20Social%20Service%20(NSS)%20(2021-22)%E2%80%94the%20first-ever%20recipient%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Best%20Forest%20Friend%20Award%20by%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Social%20Forestry%20Department%20for%20his%20large-scale%20tree-planting%20initiatives.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Ambassador%20of%20Humanity%20Award%20(2024).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Global%2